OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with rain, persistent at
OL,6,Ftimes. This soon turns to patchy
OL,7,Fdrizzle as bright spells develop in
OL,8,Fthe morning. Many places become dry
OL,9,Fwith bright or sunny spells as the
OL,10,Fdrizzle clears to the occasional
OL,11,Fshower from mid-morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBright or clear spells
OL,14,Fcontinue as showers die during the
OL,15,Fevening. Cloud will increase as
OL,16,Foutbreaks of locally heavy rain spread
OL,17,Fnortheast towards morning.
OL,18,
OL,19,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,20,Flocally heavy rain. This rain becomes
OL,21,Fpatchy from the late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
