OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,6,Fof locally heavy rain Friday clears to
OL,7,Fpatchy and showery rain Saturday. The
OL,8,Frain then clears overnight to leave
OL,9,FSunday dry with sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
